      <div class="project-card border rounded shadow-sm p-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
        <h2>ARMv7 vs RISC-V architectures</h2>
        <img src="/images/risc-vs-arm.jpg" alt="RISC-V vs ARMv7 Diagram" class="img-fluid rounded mb-2">
        <p>This project compares ARMv7 and RISC-V architectures through hands-on assembly programming exercises. We implemented a calculator on ARMv7 and a Fibonacci generator on RISC-V, analyzing instruction sets and performance.</p>
        <a href="/documents/armv7-riscv-report.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm">View Full Report</a>
      </div>

